snippet.title: Jade's Ascension - Trailer - PlayStation 4 (English)
snippet.description:
Jade's Ascension is a local cooperative arcade game based on Chinese mythology, in which players must coordinate to overcome different rooms full of enemies to reach the highest floor of the tower. 


Will you be the next emperor of Mojolonia? 🐉


Available at PlayStation 4! 🎮
